metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 啊。。哪有热自来水", "timestamp": 1616559194, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不能", "timestamp": 1616559219, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321648, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以要从六楼下到一楼打洗脚水？都花钱了怎么用不是自己的事吗？这个和环境又有啥关系。。。", "timestamp": 1616559228, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 因为直饮水不是生活用水，起码作用不是这样。每生产一顿直饮水要排掉1.5顿不能做任何回收利用的生活污水。", "timestamp": 1616559274, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实浪费，但我不相信真的会有人为了不浪费水而愿意端着洗脚盆从四楼跑到一楼接水", "timestamp": 1616559274, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321656, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 是的，直饮水0.4，加热水0.32", "timestamp": 1616559283, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321657, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 其实可以，但是比直饮水水质差", "timestamp": 1616559296, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 祝你以后喝不上水。", "timestamp": 1616559308, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321669, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "打起来！打起来！好耶！快！", "timestamp": 1616559436, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321673, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "吵起来！吵起来！互不理解，消灭对方不就好了！", "timestamp": 1616559466, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321682, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 完全不懂，我就是一个倡议。也是，大部分月花销四五千的人，哪里会在意环境和能源如何。", "timestamp": 1616559592, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321686, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 可爱的Kate小朋友，饮水机原则上不让用这种大敞口的东西接水的。热水壶打回去，然后自己添加热水冷水不香嘛", "timestamp": 1616559650, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321690, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 无关，你尽情浪费。花钱就行。", "timestamp": 1616559683, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321710, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好耶！好耶！Kate和Alice，快来！", "timestamp": 1616559915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321711, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自己人斗什么斗，学校增加几个普通的热水器不是解决问题的关键吗", "timestamp": 1616559940, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321716, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不好意思，热水壶我也不愿意从四楼跑到一楼打水", "timestamp": 1616559994, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321720, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上面的人就希望底下的人为这种事争吵呢，吵也吵不出什么结果，他们还不用为此增加预算", "timestamp": 1616560032, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1321752, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 259968, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那应该去哪接水呀